results.name: Permutation of natural numbers induced by the Catalan bijection gmA074682! acting on the parenthesizations encoded by A014486/A063171.
link: A. Karttunen, Gatomorphisms (with the complete Scheme source)
Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
program: (Scheme function implementing this automorphism on list-structures:)
(define (gmA074682! s) (cond ((pair? s) (gmA074682! (car s)) (gmA074682! (cdr s)) (gmrobr! s))) s)
